## The Class CoopGameBase 
The virtual class `CoopGameBase` contains the game vector as attribute and is the parent class of all implemented cooperative game theory concepts. It provides one setter and one getter for the game vector.
The game vector object itself can be definied manually or created by the help of coalition functions which implement the virtual class `CoopGameCFunc` and are discussed in the following section.